{"type": "article", "id": 16365, "title": "“咚咚”灯", "description": "", "date": "2015-10-21T06:58:45Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 161922, "comment_count": 3, "praise_count": 70, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160606135734W7TQFo5kdMKLyIl2.jpg", "contents": "\n\n<p>\r\n\t来自柏林的设计师 Fabien Dumas 为西班牙的照明品牌 marset 推出他改良版的灯饰“咚咚”（tam tam）。外形有些像打击乐器，可以任意调整灯罩的方向，让光源发散开来，配合彩色的灯罩，是非常活泼的组合。新系列包括一组落地灯和吊灯，都是在一根金属杆上随意转动，适合酒吧，餐厅或家庭等私人空间。<a href=\"http://www.marset.com/en/lamps/tam-tam/\" target=\"_blank\">点击这里可以查看更多信息。</a>\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160726143654AO3XSW498FxmYBnw.jpg\" width=\"818\" height=\"896\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"1.09535452\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/201607261436552hiePHQZJwYr56LU.jpg\" width=\"818\" height=\"544\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.66503667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160726143656A6okfiQPtB53dLFG.jpg\" width=\"818\" height=\"939\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"1.14792176\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160726143656x0bEK3zcRsNIYO5d.jpg\" width=\"818\" height=\"909\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"1.11124694\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160726143657hZFfNUtqG6E9Jdp2.jpg\" width=\"818\" height=\"544\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.66503667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\n\n\n\n"}